          "shippingOptions": {
            "type": "array",
            "description": "A list that defines the seller's shipping configurations for DOMESTIC and INTERNATIONAL order shipments. shippingOptions is a list with a single element if the seller ships to only domestic locations. If the seller also ships internationally, the list contains a second element that defines their international shipping options. Shipping options configure the high-level shipping settings that apply to orders, such as flat-rate or calculated shipping, any rate tables the seller wants to associate with the shipping services, plus other details (such as the shippingServices offered for domestic or international shipments).",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ShippingOption"
