          "wasPreviouslyOptedIn": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "If set to true, the seller was at one point opted-in to the associated payment program, but they later opted out of the program. A value of false indicates the seller never opted-in to the program or if they did opt-in to the program, they never opted-out of it. It's important to note that the setting of this field does not indicate the seller's current status regarding the payment program. It is possible for this field to return true while the status field returns OPTED_IN."
          }
