            "description": "A two-letter ISO 3166-1 Alpha-2 country code representing the eBay marketplace where an item is listed. For implementation help, refer to <a href='https://developer.ebay.com/devzone/rest/api-ref/account/types/CountryCodeEnum.html'>eBay API documentation</a>"
